<div class="bg-red-800 text-white py-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">ðŸš¨ Emergency Hotlines & Directory</h1>
    <p class="text-red-200 mt-1">Important contact numbers for emergencies and public safety</p>
